<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Eratosthenes's Measure of the Earth's Circumference</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root {
