<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Heat Equation: Collocation vs Analytical</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-latest.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --panel: #f3f3f3;
      --border: #e0e0e0;
      --grid: #dddddd;
      --text: #222;
      --accent: #2b7cff;
