        Red graphics show the encoded output: a two-level square wave for ASDM or spike trains for IAF.
        Axes ticks are spaced at 0.5 units; the time axis range follows your selected window.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div id="control-panel">
      <div class="row">
        <label for="slider-start-time">start time</label>
        <input type="range" id="slider-start-time" min="-5" max="5" step="0.1" value="-1.0">
